<section class="template-show">
  <header class="templates__header">
    <h1><%= h(@template.name) %></h1>
    <p class="templates__hint">
      파일: <code><%= h(@template.path.relative_path_from(Sowing::Infrastructure::Paths.vault_dir)) %></code>
    </p>
    <p>
      <a href="/templates" class="button button--secondary">← 목록</a>
    </p>
  </header>

  <article class="template-show__pane">
    <h2>원본 (placeholder 포함)</h2>
    <pre class="template-show__source"><%= h(@template.content) %></pre>
  </article>

  <article class="template-show__pane">
    <h2>미리보기 (현재 시각으로 치환)</h2>
    <pre class="template-show__rendered"><%= h(@rendered) %></pre>
  </article>
</section>
